title: Casino Slots 1.5.4 -3D Game
description:
Try your luck at slot machines in this 3D environment. LastEnd Casino Slots has Random Number Generators which are continually generating so the game play is always changing. This is a nice way to try out your luck on slot machines without using real money. 

Contains 3 Slot Designs
Hot 7 slot is a 3 reel set at $0.01 value, VRS Slot is a 3 reel set a $1 value, and Lucky Farm Slot is a 5 reel set a multiple values. Each shot can be play by using the slot lever or by hitting the spin button. The bet can be changed by using multiplier buttons, this allow you to change the bet from 1-10. 

Casino Slots features an online high scoreboard that allow you to compare your luck and skill against other players from around the world. To uses this scoreboard look for the cash out A.T.M. located in the main game room
